  description="Terms of use for Assembling Me."
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 py-24" id="main-content">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
      <p>
        This site is provided for reading, reference, and general information. Content may change
        without notice as posts are edited, corrected, or expanded.
      </p>
      <h2>No warranty</h2>
      <p>
        Material on this site is provided as-is. Technical posts may describe experiments, tooling,
        or opinions and should be evaluated before you rely on them in production.
      </p>
      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>
        Some pages link to third-party sites such as GitHub. Those sites operate under their own
        terms and privacy policies.
      </p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about site use can be sent to <a href="mailto:tenner.joshua@gmail.com">tenner.joshua@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
</EditorialLayout>
